<p itemprop="description">Strategic thinking involves analyzing complex situations, understanding long-term implications, and developing comprehensive plans that align with organizational goals and government objectives.</p>

<div class="proficiency-levels">
    <h2>Proficiency Levels</h2>

    <ol class="skill-levels">
        <li>
            <h3>Awareness</h3>
            <p>You can understand the importance of strategic thinking and recognise strategic considerations in government decision-making and planning processes.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h3>Working</h3>
            <p>You can contribute to strategic planning activities, understand organizational strategy, and align your work with strategic objectives and priorities.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h3>Practitioner</h3>
            <p>You can develop strategic plans, analyze complex problems, anticipate future trends, and provide strategic guidance to teams and projects.</p>
        </li>
        <li>
            <h3>Expert</h3>
            <p>You can lead strategic thinking across organizations, influence government policy, and drive transformational change through strategic vision and planning.</p>
        </li>
    </ol>
</div>

